tiles.query:
fetch logs //, scanLimitGBytes: 500, samplingRatio: 1000
| filter k8s.namespace.name=="argocd" and k8s.deployment.name=="argocd-server-*" and status=="ERROR"
| sort timestamp desc

fetch logs //, scanLimitGBytes: 500, samplingRatio: 1000
| filter k8s.namespace.name=="argocd" and k8s.deployment.name=="argocd-repo-server-*" and status=="ERROR"
| sort timestamp desc

fetch logs //, scanLimitGBytes: 500, samplingRatio: 1000
| filter k8s.namespace.name=="argocd" and status=="ERROR" and k8s.deployment.name=="argocd-application-controller-*"
| sort timestamp desc

fetch logs //, scanLimitGBytes: 500, samplingRatio: 1000
| filter k8s.namespace.name=="argocd" and status=="ERROR" and k8s.deployment.name=="argocd-redis-ha-server-*"
| sort timestamp desc

fetch logs //, scanLimitGBytes: 500, samplingRatio: 1000
| filter k8s.namespace.name=="argocd" and status=="ERROR" and k8s.deployment.name=="argocd-redis-ha-haproxy-*"
| sort timestamp desc

fetch logs //, scanLimitGBytes: 500, samplingRatio: 1000
| filter k8s.namespace.name=="argocd" and k8s.deployment.name=="argocd-notifications-controller-*" and not contains(content, "Failed to notify recipient") OR NOT contains(content, "failed to execute when condition: cannot fetch phase from") and status=="ERROR"
| fields timestamp, status, content
| sort timestamp desc

fetch logs //, scanLimitGBytes: 500, samplingRatio: 1000
| filter k8s.namespace.name=="argocd" and status=="ERROR" and k8s.deployment.name=="argocd-applicationset-controller-*"
| sort timestamp desc
